PrecisAppointment of certain persons as alternate Commissioners of the Canadian Section of the Pacific Salmon Commission, for a term of four years. (Bud Graham, West Vancouver, British Columbia, in the place of Alan F. Lill, whose term has expired; Bill Lefeaux-Valentine, Victoria, British Columbia, in the place of Stefani Paine, whose term has expired; Hubert Haldane, Prince Rupert, British Columbia, in the place of Nelson Keitlah, whose term has expired; and Mike Hunter, North Vancouver, British Columbia, in the place of Jack Nichol, whose term has expired)
